Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>、おとなしく 待ってるかな……？
Entry.EnglishText: Do you think <Tytree> is waiting patiently back there?

Entry.JapaneseText: さあな……迷惑をかけて いなければいいが……
Entry.EnglishText: Who knows... Hopefully he's not causing any problems...

Entry.JapaneseText: 心配するくらいなら、 連れてきた方がよかったかもネ？
Entry.EnglishText: Well, if you're that worried, maybe we should go back and grab him?
